afterimage composition, ghost-like trailing duplicate creating sense of prior motion
bordered composition, decorative frame around the image for structured presentation
bust chart layout, character portraits showing head and shoulders in organized grid
character chart layout, multiple poses or expressions of one character on a sheet
collage composition, overlapping images and elements assembled into unified artwork
column lineup layout, characters or elements arranged in vertical columns
cropped composition, tightly framed subject with elements extending beyond image edges
diagram style, annotated technical illustration with labels and measurement lines
fading border, image edges gradually blend to white or transparent for soft transition
feet out of frame, subject cropped at ankles for intimate mid-body framing
framed composition, visible picture frame surrounding the artwork for gallery display look
glitch composition, digital artifacts and data corruption creating experimental visual chaos
golden ratio composition, elements arranged along the mathematical spiral for natural balance
head out of frame, subject cropped at neck for mysterious or body-focused composition
isometric perspective, 30-degree angled view without vanishing point for technical clarity
leading lines composition, converging lines guiding the eye toward the focal point
letterboxed format, black horizontal bars creating widescreen cinema aspect ratio
lineup composition, characters or elements standing side by side for comparison or display
mosaic art composition, image divided into grid of smaller images forming larger picture
movement chart, sequential poses showing stages of an action or transformation
negative space composition, empty areas actively shaping the subject for minimalist impact
omake bonus content, extra illustration or sketch added as supplementary artwork
out of frame composition, subject partially extending beyond the image boundaries
outside border, elements breaking through the frame edge for dynamic layered effect
split underwater composition, half above and half below water surface
photomosaic, larger image assembled from hundreds of smaller photographs
pillarboxed format, black vertical bars on sides creating narrow vertical frame
polar opposites composition, contrasting elements placed in direct visual opposition
projected inset, smaller image overlaid within the main scene for detail or context
reference sheet, multiple views and details of a character for design documentation
relationship chart, connected portraits showing character connections and bonds
rotational symmetry, image elements repeating in circular rotation around center point
rounded corners, softened image edges for modern and friendly visual presentation
rule of thirds composition, key elements placed at grid intersection points for balance
seating arrangement, characters positioned in organized seated formation
social media layout, optimized framing for sharing on digital platforms
stats overlay, numerical or graphical data displayed alongside the visual content
symmetrical composition, mirrored balance along a central axis for structured harmony
tachi-e standing portrait, full-body character illustration on transparent background
trim marks, printing crop guides visible at corners for professional print layout
viewfinder overlay, camera viewfinder frame with focus points and exposure information
zoom layer, magnified detail inset showing close-up of specific area within the scene
